Symbol.Script_1D:

dim stSlideTypes[2] stSlideTypes[1] = `Пластик` stSlideTypes[2] = `Металл`
dim aDefaultHeights[6] aDefaultHeights[1] = 2.27 aDefaultHeights[2] = 2.63 aDefaultHeights[3] = 2.99 aDefaultHeights[4] = 3.35 aDefaultHeights[5] = 3.71 aDefaultHeights[6] = 4.07
riserHeight = 0.36 riserRad = 0.015 beamThk = 0.1 topHeight = 0.83
plateThk = 0.02 plateRoundRad = 0.05 sidePlateWidth = 0.35 sidePlateHeight = topHeight * 0.9
frontPlateHeight = 0.15 frontPlateWidth = A - beamThk frontPlateRad = 0.35
slideHeight = ZZYZX - topHeight ladderAngle = 20 ladderDistance = tan(ladderAngle) * (ZZYZX - topHeight / 4) ladderLength = sqr(ladderDistance^2 + (ZZYZX - topHeight / 4)^2) ladderWidth = A - beamThk * 2 - plateThk * 2 riserLength = ladderWidth - beamThk
slideTopLength = 0.2 slideBottomLength = 0.3 slideBottomHeight = 0.2
platformDepth = (topHeight * 0.75) * tan(ladderAngle) + beamThk platformWidth = riserLength platformThk = riserRad * 2
slideSideWidth = ladderWidth slideSideHeight = 0.2 slideBottomWidth = platformWidth slideBottomThk = platformThk slideRoundRad = (slideSideWidth - slideBottomWidth) / 2
slideBendRad1 = 0.3 slideBendRad2 = 1
sidePanelRad = topHeight * 0.7 ladderPanelHeight = sqr(riserHeight^2 + (tan(ladderAngle)*riserHeight)^2) sideOffset = 0.4
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "iSlideType" SLIDETYPE_PLASTIC, stSlideTypes[1], SLIDETYPE_METAL, stSlideTypes[2]
values "nRisers" 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8
values "A" range [0.5,0.97] lock "B", "ZZYZX"
if iSlideType = SLIDETYPE_PLASTIC then parameters B = ladderDistance + (slideHeight - slideBottomHeight) / tan(35) + slideBottomLength + 0.05 + beamThk / 2 + sideOffset
hideparameter "matWood", "matMetalSlide", "matPlastic" endif
if iSlideType = SLIDETYPE_METAL then parameters B = ladderDistance + (slideHeight - slideBottomHeight) / tan(35) + slideBottomLength + 0.05 + beamThk / 2
hideparameter "matFrame", "matPlasticLadder", "matPlasticSlide" endif
parameters ZZYZX = aDefaultHeights[nRisers - 2]
